    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2150619429" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8790672022256439685">Another great story telling of Ancient Rome. This one is more about the politics surrounding the Catiline conspiracy (<a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_'>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_</a>...), but Gordianus is still in the game to Find. </span>
  <span id="freeText8790672022256439685" style="display:none">Another great story telling of Ancient Rome. This one is more about the politics surrounding the Catiline conspiracy (<a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Second_</a>...), but Gordianus is still in the game to Find. </span>
  <a data-text-id="8790672022256439685" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


